{"tid":1801223,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"唯一解決目前矛盾方法：立即落實2020雙普選","createTime":"2019-12-28T12:42:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-28T12:42:18.000Z","uid":112185,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"53bce48e835a77dd0d8443d271599788a99bc197","tid":1801223,"uid":112185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T12:42:18.000Z","msg":"其實淨返有啲咩都唔洗講，藍黃左右都好，有乜野就叫民選執政者同民選議員處理。<br />\n<br />\n普選都仆街既話，自己㨂，唔會再投訴，下任再選過。<br />\n<br />\n我要藍同黃都知：<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\"><strong>「立即實行雙普選，香港唯一出路。」</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"color: navy;\">靜靜雞贏：香港獨立，唯一出路。先普選，再公投</span></span>"}]}